Reasoning: The paper discusses the robustness of networks, specifically the backbone Internet, which falls under the category of network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also mentions attacks and failures, which suggests a focus on security (cs.CR). Additionally, the use of metrics and modeling suggests a focus on systems and information (cs.SI) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the perspective of both infrastructure and users, which could fall under the category of cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
